{"tid":1615903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際戰線升級]入嚟聽下我講，一起叫外國人罷賣！","createTime":"2019-10-03T08:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T11:15:39.000Z","uid":326820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1dc50751b125fa3bab3f5f8379d305cafa26fff2","tid":1615903,"uid":326820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:41:02.000Z","msg":"各位手足，第一次開po，有錯麻煩屌得細力啲。<br />\n<br />\n我哋自己罷賣嘅行動威力一直有限，啲奶共公司都唔太怕我哋。因為香港人嘅market好有限，所以我哋要將罷賣嘅行動升級， <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推俾外國人一齊做</span></span></strong> ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個行動嘅最大好處係可以係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">經濟方面重創中國</span></strong></span> ，令大陸嘅 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際籌碼同鎮壓香港嘅本錢減少</span></span></strong> ！只要呢個行動可以令少少人罷賣，大陸嘅經濟損失係幾何級咁上！因為一個人嘅收入係佢嘅支出，即係另一個人嘅收入，所以 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個經濟損失係會滾雪球咁滾大</span></span></strong> ！而且消費模式係習慣性嘅，佢哋習慣咗唔買中國貨，個習慣就會維持，繼而令經濟損失更大！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，呢個行動可以 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">增加外國人嘅參與度</span></span></strong> 。一直以嚟，當外國人問佢哋有咩可以做嘅時候，我哋最多只係可以答咩寫信俾啲政棍，簽下petition咁。有呢個行動，我哋就可以大大聲同佢講， <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你可以罷賣中國貨以示支持</span></span></strong> ！當佢哋一直以罷賣嘅方式參與我哋嘅抗爭，佢哋就會自然覺得係我哋嘅一份子，自然會更留意香港嘅新聞，更加上心。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行動嘅成本亦都好低</span></span></strong> ，只需要 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">英文文宣</span></span></strong> 幫下手，再搵本身做緊國際戰線嘅手足同大家係各大社交媒體 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推俾外國人睇</span></span></strong> 就可以，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">完全唔需要留血被捕</span></span></strong>，非常簡單。<br />\n<br />\n為左鼓勵各手足幫手推動個campaign，我諗咗啲切入點亦做咗啲文宣，但係我唔識photoshop，所以係用powerpoint整出嚟，所以唔係好靚，請見諒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/um7VYs4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fum7VYs4.png&h=72221c37&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CuEty1q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCuEty1q.png&h=07f7ab27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. 同啲外國人講：大陸做咁多唔人道嘅事，你唔係仲俾錢佢呀嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ni9QNmz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNi9QNmz.jpg&h=768514d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 同啲外國人講： 支持香港／自由嘅，就一齊杯葛中國啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDAgHU0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDAgHU0.jpg&h=92d35f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. 用一啲中共大品牌做切入點，我呢度用華為做例子，但係都可以用阿里巴巴咁，自己發揮下創意<br />\n<br />\n只要係文宣上加 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[#BoycottChinazi]</span></span></strong> 就可以達到campaign嘅效果 (我知有啲手足好忌葦用chinazi呢個字，但我諗咗好耐覺得呢個hashtag最簡潔最易明，唔鍾意嘅可以用#BoycottChina或者#Boycott_For_HK)<br />\n<br />\n最後，大家要留意嘅幾點係， <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要用香港／大陸嘅唔人道嘅理由做切入點</span></span></strong> ，例如華為係有好多監聽，資料外洩問題，但係 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個campaign個attention要係香港度</span></span></strong> ，所以避免以中國其他問題叫人罷賣，因為咁樣啲外國人關注嘅就唔會係香港。<br />\n<br />\n求大家幫手推，幫手做文宣，唔止英文要有，日文、法文、西班牙文、乜嘢文我都要見到！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權 打倒中共！<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2c1469e9c7044917caacacae95790ad9f88f5e58","tid":1615903,"uid":326820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:41:31.000Z","msg":"推1<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ad9e7ae24431d58fce563840023493bdbdfbbfb6","tid":1615903,"uid":326820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:41:49.000Z","msg":"推2<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"338264bb5d5c4d19ce2960227e58d8172a2ccf78","tid":1615903,"uid":326820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:42:00.000Z","msg":"推3<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"66d9da367da96d06dadca8b0c624a9d86ef8d7da","tid":1615903,"uid":326820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:42:12.000Z","msg":"推4<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2ef27c7b4e6495547c9f3e394360b05700ad9dda","tid":1615903,"uid":326820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"推5<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"bb6d942993e856b326f0d8c2dfe2416dcd6fe9bb","tid":1615903,"uid":326820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:47:24.000Z","msg":"推6<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"374328529dac263bc157fd10670e684caf41a67d","tid":1615903,"uid":309137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:15:39.000Z","msg":"好同意，我都有出過po想搞外國罷買，奈何真係推唔郁。<br />\n其實外國罷買中國貨係echos到而家爆紅鋪的理念。<br />\n希望多d人睇到"}]}